      "writtenOn": "2020-05-19T13:47:04Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I\u0027m confused about this change. We are not every using the ID3D12PipelineState returned by this besides just putting in directly into a GrD3DPipelineState object. So why not leave the original Make function. Within that make function you can obviously pull out a private helper function to make the ID3D12PipelineState but I don\u0027t see any reason for this to be a public factory here.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 26,
        "startChar": 3,
        "endLine": 33,
        "endChar": 94
      },
      "revId": "ef77a24b7cc6c5983be5ef3c1d74d58da8d96f94",
