        "id": 5065
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-05-19T14:46:39Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "This was to avoid having a giant parameter list, because I\u0027ll have to pass through the additional params to the GrD3DPipelineState constructor to store the uniforms, processors, etc.  I also considered making it a private static function in GrD3DPipelineStateBuilder, if that works better.",
      "parentUuid": "e2cc4581_a093efb1",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 26,
        "startChar": 3,
        "endLine": 33,
        "endChar": 94
      },
      "revId": "ef77a24b7cc6c5983be5ef3c1d74d58da8d96f94",
